node.text:
i’ve held onto this song for more than a year and I can’t be more proud of a record. I’m so happy that this is dropping —  it’s been my favorite project and such a dope music video as well. I wanted to remind y’all that I wouldn’t be able to do what I do today without you. Teenage Heartbreak the album is my greatest creation and here’s the first sprinkle of it. Let’s get it started babyyy🖤
“Partycrasher” music video directed by @mooch is out now only on my @facebook !!
